        &lt;executions&gt;
          &lt;execution&gt;
            &lt;id&gt;make-assembly&lt;/id&gt;
            &lt;phase&gt;package&lt;/phase&gt;
            &lt;goals&gt;
              &lt;goal&gt;single&lt;/goal&gt;
            &lt;/goals&gt;
          &lt;/execution&gt;
        &lt;/executions&gt;
      &lt;/plugin&gt;
```

and then run -
```
mvn clean package 
