If you cancel the _age_ input dialog it will return _null_.  
And, passing a _null_ argument to _[Integer#parseInt](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/Integer.html#parseInt(java.lang.String))_ will produce a _[NumberFormatException](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/NumberFormatException.html)_.

```none
