```

Here is the source for _Integer#parseInt_.  
_[GitHub &amp;ndash; jdk/src/java.base/share/classes/java/lang/Integer.java](https://github.com/openjdk/jdk/blob/master/src/java.base/share/classes/java/lang/Integer.java#L623)_.

```java
