```

You&#39;ll need to check for _null_.  
I suggest using the _Integer_ and _Double_ classes, you can utilize the _null_ assignment.

```java
String name = JOptionPane.showInputDialog (&quot;Enter your name&quot;);
JOptionPane.showMessageDialog (null, &quot;Hello &quot; + name);

Integer age = null;
